		<part id="conclusions">
			<title>Conclusions</title>
			<slide id="long-game">
				<title>Focus on the Long Game</title>
				<ul>
					<li>Look at everything within the bigger context</li>
					<li>Never be afraid to ask <em>what</em> the goal is and <em>why</em></li>
					<li>Always keep in mind that <em>everything digital needs to scale</em></li>
					<li>Watch out for lack of vision (rarely) and strategy (routinely)</li>
				</ul>
